ygData.messageBody:
i haven't found any necro quest but i have solve some general quests and
warrior quests.
1.Kill RedV robot in newbie dungeon and u get scrap metal and
blackbox...give scrap metal to the merchant outside of dungeon..and u get
money .About the blackbox i heard it's a warrior quest item but i am not
sure.
2.blackbox found on clcokwork...return it to the warrior guide to the
armored man and he will give u faction/money.
3. Kill Gearheart robot at lesser faydark(near border) and return the
blackbox to warrior guidemaster(the old lady).
